h2. Awaken

h3. Description from source:

It's been a while since I posted anything here, I'm sorry if its been like that. I've been busy with a lot of things in life, specially when Typhoon Rammasun(Glenda) hit us here in the Philippines. Our roofing got damaged, everything got wet even my computer & tablet.
Luckily everything seems to be working perfectly & we got things fix around here.
At least now It's nice to get back to art again, I'll do my best to finish more artworks soon and get things done around. ^^
Thanks for everything!
SPEED PAINT:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iq5pse79U3k
Tools: SAI, PS & Cintiq 13HD
Time: About 15 hours for 3 days.
Other Accounts:
http://thanshuhai.deviantart.com/
http://livestream.com/thanshuhai
https://twitter.com/thanshuhai
https://www.youtube.com/thanshuhai
https://toebeanies.com/

The end of this story.

Once again, these pages were made thanks to Vavacung, one of our patreon patrons. Thank you for your continued support!
